1. *Vragu* ne dam da mi oduzmu slobodu. (I won't let the devil take away my freedom.)
2. Rekao sam mu da ode u *vraga*. (I told him to go to hell.)
3. Ne znam šta je sa njim, u poslednje vreme se ponaša kao da ga je *vrag* odneo. (I don't know what's wrong with him, lately he's been acting like the devil took him.)
4. *Vrag* je odneo šalu. (The devil took the joke.)
5. Ne mogu da se koncentrišem, *vrag* me tera da razmišljam o drugim stvarima. (I can't concentrate, the devil makes me think about other things.)
6. Moramo da se borimo protiv *vraga* koji nas napada. (We have to fight against the devil that's attacking us.)
7. *Vragu* nećemo dati da nam uništi snove. (We won't let the devil destroy our dreams.)